***Why "Tulsa"?
The name "Tulsa" represents a fresh start and honest approach to creator business management - built on integrity, transparency, and respect for both creators and their audiences.
Support & Contribution
This is an open system designed to be:
Modified to fit your needs
Extended with new features
Integrated with your existing tools
Shared with other creators
Technical Excellence
Built with:
✅ Type safety (Rust)
✅ Async operations (Tokio)
✅ RESTful design
✅ Responsive UI
✅ Clean architecture
✅ Comprehensive error handling
✅ Database indexing for performance
***Remember: Tulsa is a tool to help you manage your creator business more effectively. The relationships, content, and engagement are still yours - Tulsa just helps you stay organized and make informed decisions.
